Author: Orozu.ORO
Title: [ANN] Orozu (ORO) - Our ICO is Live
Body: Hi welytomi  With this team you know that we will constantly push the limits to increase the price of our coin with more liquidity and utility propositions. We created the coin with a very clear objective which are  1. Why it is a coin and not a token,we have our own blockchain 2. We don't have a big supply which is beneficial for investors as more demand and adoption the more the price increases 3. Coin is a hybrid our POW has been completed and now it is on POS as POS as known to decentralize the whole eco system which is a better system 4. We are now in talks with many exchanges and other than closing a crypto to crypto exchange, we also understand the important of our coin to have fiat to crypto trading pairs. We have closed 2 exchanges with fiat to crypto trading pairs which we will roll out after we rolled out our crypto to crypto exchange for us to qualify to be in coinmarketcap. 5. We have a trading/lending program which is fair and we took a lot of time thinking and testing when developing it. We do not guarantee returns and you can only lend 50% of your total coins for risk management purpose. To top it of , we have spoken to an insurance company that will secure all our investors of the whole amount lend against mishandling and misappropriation. Our trading/ lending program carries a securities license which is stated in our website. 6. We have a 24 hr/7 days a week chat support for you to be in contact with us for any problems you face  There are many more reasons i could tell you which are amazing for our supporters/investors/community but i would just end to tell you that the whole plan was carefully planned so that it could benefit the whole community and our team will not stop working to make this coin one of the top coin in the market.

Author: olkah
Title: [ANN] Orozu (ORO) - Our ICO is Live
Body: Orozu Initial Coin Offering is extended from its onset in February together with Web Wallet and DDOS Attack Protection this year. Crypto enthusiasts are eager to know the outcome of the initial launching. As this major event comes to a close in due time, crypto users will share as much anticipation for Orozu Exchange and Lending Program which is next on its roadmap.  Following this, the Orozu External Exchange Trading and onboarding of an insurance company to cover all its lending will take place. This will provide insurance solutions to the companys lending-related activities before Orozu gets listed in the Coinmarketcap by May 2018.  With the emergence of new crypto coins, users have become more meticulous of their choices for coin investment. Orozu shows strength with its continuing stability since its test-run on crypto trading in June of last year. The coins value has increased by 25% even as its ICO is still ongoing and is highly optimistic to have a steady progression on its agenda to improve its features the entire year.  Along with its IOS/Android Wallet-launching in May, Upgrade on Security in June and Onboarding of External FIAT to Crypto Exchange in July, other planned improvements are on its calendar all the way to 2019. Orozu is projected to be in the Top 10 on Coinmarketcap by January 2019 and onwards to become one of the major currencies of the 21st century. Orozu is definitely strong and on its way to perfecting its coin. Taking the Orozu opportunity is the smart choice for todays scrupulous investor. Check out www.orozu.com to know quite a number of good reasons why.
